DARK PSYCHOLOGY
While talking w someone, pay attention his/her eye color, Eye contact makes you likeable
Stay calm in a discussion, probably they would get angrier but then they would blame themselves
people who refused a big favour, then they feel they should approve a smaller favour. %50 discount they say no, but %30 to persuade
when you see someone, you really look happy and excited, they also feel like the same way. Dogs use this trick
Chew a gum to decrease stress or being nervous or eat. Primitive brain will be convinced it isnt in danger.
Dont use I think or I believe. these words shows lack of self-confidence


